{"tid":2244053,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國國務院詳列加強制裁港共官員理由: 押後立會選舉, 引國安法拉人....","createTime":"2020-10-15T08:05:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-15T10:19:46.000Z","uid":134071,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"591b9cb7466206267d725863023dd80072ae3e65","tid":2244053,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:05:44.000Z","msg":"只貼其中三位:<br />\n<br />\n<em>夏寶龍<br />\n<br />\n港澳辦主任，為北京實施其香港政策的主要人物之一，負責監督港澳辦推廣中央政府對港原則及政策，包括港區國安法。在夏寶龍領導下，港澳辦採取了一系列干預香港自治的行動，包括發表聲明宣稱它有權監督香港內政，違反《基本法》和《中英聯合聲明》。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥<br />\n<br />\n香港特首，她於2020年6月簽署港區國安法使其生效。身為特首，她同時是港區國安委主席。<strong>任內她行使過緊急權力限制香港居民的權利及自由，包括將原定2020年9月舉行的立法會選舉延遲一年。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鄧炳強<br />\n<br />\n香港警務處處長，<strong>警務處在他領導下引用港區國安法拘捕支持民主社運人士，包括在國安法生效24小時內被捕的10人。鄧炳強也是港區國安委成員。</strong><br />\n<br />\n美國國務院網頁</em><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201015/AYBHJWR5NBBMNP7ERQ7OC7IBEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201015%2FAYBHJWR5NBBMNP7ERQ7OC7IBEY%2F&d=1vxPP2MBW0T8%2FIxNX4ugztAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=5fc41243\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201015%2FAYBHJWR5NBBMNP7ERQ7OC7IBEY%2F&h=536207d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201015/AYBHJWR5NBBMNP7ERQ7OC7IBEY/</a>"},{"pid":"5a251d7507e37a358f0a5b1c4549f14e34c34455","tid":2244053,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:06:30.000Z","msg":"邊個仲話初選無用?&nbsp;&nbsp;初選令林鄭押後選舉. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decc617af5997bf060c603800d9590ad5a547306","tid":2244053,"uid":67065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5a251d7507e37a358f0a5b1c4549f14e34c34455","tid":2244053,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T08:06:30.000Z","msg":"邊個仲話初選無用?&nbsp;&nbsp;初選